Class CareerStaff

java.lang.Object
CareerStaff
All Implemented Interfaces:
IUser, Serializable
public class CareerStaff extends Object implements IUser
Represents a career services staff user in the internship portal. A CareerStaff user can log in to the system and is identified by an ID, name, role, department and email. The password is stored in hashed form for security.
